('chk-ui-automation-review', 'ph-ui-automation', 90, 'checkpoint', 'gate', NULL, NULL, 'UI Automation Review Gate', 'Review checkpoint for UI Automation and End-to-End Testing. The learner consolidates evidence from E2E Test Scope and Strategy, Selectors and Locators, Waits and Synchronization, Page Object Model and Screenplay Pattern, identifies unresolved prerequisite gaps, and decides whether to continue, review selected topics, or complete extra practice before the next roadmap segment.', 'This checkpoint acts as a transition gate for the software quality assurance roadmap. It supports reflection and planning; it is not a certification, mastery test, or claim of job readiness.', 'checkpoint', 'ph-ui-automation', 7, 90, 2, 'intermediate', 100, NULL, NULL, '{"source": "roadmap.sh/qa", "visualRole": "checkpoint", "checkpointPurpose": "phase_review", "reviewMode": "gate", "evidenceRequired": true, "claimLimit": "orientation_and_progress_review_only_not_certification"}'::jsonb, true, true, '["Summarize the main concepts and decisions from UI Automation and End-to-End Testing in practical software quality assurance terms.", "Identify prerequisite gaps, unclear topics, or risks that should be reviewed before moving forward.", "Create a short evidence artifact that links completed roadmap items to what was learned."]'::jsonb, '["List the roadmap items reviewed for this checkpoint.", "Provide one evidence artifact such as notes, a diagram, a lab result, code, queries, screenshots, or a project review.", "Record at least two gaps, risks, or follow-up actions, or explicitly state that no critical gaps were found.", "Use the result to choose one next step: continue, review selected topics, or complete extra practice."]'::jsonb),
('proj-ui-e2e-suite', 'ph-ui-automation', 100, 'project', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Required UI End-to-End Automation Suite', 'Milestone project brief: Build a browser automation suite for core user journeys with stable selectors, reports, traces, and CI readiness. Build a reviewable data pipeline project that demonstrates the main decisions from UI Automation and End-to-End Testing. Expected evidence includes an ingest-transform-load flow, schema or data quality checks, and a run log or lineage note explaining failure handling. Keep scope focused so the result can be completed, checked, and explained.', 'This required milestone project turns the surrounding QA Engineer topics into a concrete artifact. It gives the learner a clearer target, suggested build path, and review evidence without treating completion as proof of mastery or job readiness.', 'side', 'ph-ui-automation', 7, 100, 7, 'intermediate', 100, NULL, NULL, '{"source": "roadmap.sh/qa","visualRole": "side","projectPurpose": "milestone_practice","projectKind": "data_pipeline","projectScope": "focused_milestone","evidenceRequired": true,"claimLimit": "reviewable_project_evidence_only_not_mastery_or_job_readiness","suggestedSteps": ["define source, target, and transformation rules","implement a reproducible run path","add quality checks and failure notes","document operational assumptions"],"expectedEvidence": ["an ingest-transform-load flow","schema or data quality checks","a run log or lineage note explaining failure handling"],"optionalPractice": false,"milestone": true}'::jsonb, true, true, '["Build a focused UI End-to-End Automation Suite artifact that demonstrates the main concepts from UI Automation and End-to-End Testing.","Explain the main design, data, tooling, or workflow decisions used in the project.","Validate the project with appropriate evidence such as tests, screenshots, logs, metrics, queries, or review notes.","Document setup, usage, limitations, and at least one follow-up improvement."]'::jsonb, '["A repository, notebook, dashboard, write-up, prototype, or configuration artifact is available for review.","The README or project notes state the project goal, setup steps, usage path, and expected output.","The deliverable includes an ingest-transform-load flow, schema or data quality checks, and a run log or lineage note explaining failure handling.","The learner records validation evidence such as tests, screenshots, logs, metrics, query results, playtest notes, or manual verification steps.","The review notes identify trade-offs, limitations, and one reasonable next improvement."]'::jsonb),
('proj-visual-regression-demo', 'ph-ui-automation', 111, 'project', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Visual Regression Demo', 'Optional project brief: Add screenshot-based regression checks to a small UI and document baseline review workflow. Build a small, reviewable quality engineering artifact to practice ideas from UI Automation and End-to-End Testing. Expected evidence includes a test plan or automation suite, sample defects or risk notes, and execution evidence with pass/fail output. Keep it lightweight; the goal is applied practice and clearer portfolio evidence, not a mandatory milestone.', 'This optional practice project turns the surrounding QA Engineer topics into a concrete artifact. It gives the learner a clearer target, suggested build path, and review evidence without treating completion as proof of mastery or job readiness.', 'side', 'ph-ui-automation', 7, 111, 2, 'intermediate', 100, NULL, NULL, '{"source": "roadmap.sh/qa","visualRole": "side","projectPurpose": "optional_practice","projectKind": "qa_project","projectScope": "small_practice_artifact","evidenceRequired": true,"claimLimit": "reviewable_project_evidence_only_not_mastery_or_job_readiness","suggestedSteps": ["identify risks and test targets","design manual and/or automated checks","run the checks and capture output","summarize defects and coverage gaps"],"expectedEvidence": ["a test plan or automation suite","sample defects or risk notes","execution evidence with pass/fail output"],"optionalPractice": true,"milestone": false}'::jsonb, false, true, '["Build a small Visual Regression Demo artifact to practice selected concepts from UI Automation and End-to-End Testing.","Explain the main design, data, tooling, or workflow decisions used in the project.","Validate the project with appropriate evidence such as tests, screenshots, logs, metrics, queries, or review notes.","Document setup, usage, limitations, and at least one follow-up improvement."]'::jsonb, '["A repository, notebook, dashboard, write-up, prototype, or configuration artifact is available for review.","The README or project notes state the project goal, setup steps, usage path, and expected output.","The deliverable includes a test plan or automation suite, sample defects or risk notes, and execution evidence with pass/fail output.","The learner records validation evidence such as tests, screenshots, logs, metrics, query results, playtest notes, or manual verification steps.","The review notes identify trade-offs, limitations, and one reasonable next improvement."]'::jsonb),
